 <text id="F3003T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus reports to his wife that he arrived in Charleston and immediately caught a cold. He
     also tells about seeing some of their friends from home.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
