      >se</orig> Jacop yet but i think he Will be in <orig reg="town">toan</orig>
     <orig reg="tomorrow">to Morrow</orig> and then i Will fix it With him</p>

    <p>the <orig reg="Regiment">Redgment</orig> has Camp <orig reg="outside">out side</orig> of
      <orig reg="town">toan</orig>
     <orig reg="two">too</orig> Miles But i think that <orig reg="they">tha</orig> Will stay out
      <orig reg="there">thear</orig>
     <orig reg="awhile">a While</orig> and <orig reg="If">Ife</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="Do">Dow</orig>
